body.name: Pyle 32-inch HD LED TV - 728p Monitor with DVD/CD Multimedia Disk Combo, HDMI, RCA, Headphone Jack, Speakers, Remote, Wall Mount - Works for Gaming, Streaming, PC/Mac Includes Remote Control
features: HD 768p SUPPORT: The DLED TV features an HD 1366x768p widescreen hi-res display creating a more expansive spectrum of colors and more realistic picture with a massive 32” screen size. Offers 178° vertical, 178° horizontal viewing angles

WORKS WITH PC: The HD LED TV allows you to stream audio, as well as view image collections easily. The HD TV is compatible and works well with both Mac and PC. It features selectable multi-viewing display modes such as 16:9, 4:3, zoom, and cinema

MOUNTS ON WALL: Allows you to save space in your home and opt for a clean design with the LED TV monitor. The removable base stand makes mounting to the wall a simple process. Features universal VESA mounting compatibility (200mm x 100mm)

INPUT/OUTPUT INTERFACE: The HD TV boasts built-in full range stereo speakers. The input interface has included HDMI, CVBS, RCA (L/R) audio, VGA/PC, PC audio, RF (antenna), and output interface - COAX audio, headphones, line out (analogue) audio

UPGRADED FEATURES: The LED TV screen features a slot-in DVD player, V-chip, closed caption option, bottom panel one button access & sleep timer functions. Also included in the set is a full function LED TV remote control that includes 2 AAA batteries
